room_title: Escape room "The Unknown (Part 1)" by ESCAPEability in Las Vegas
room_address: 3100 S Durango Dr, Suite 106 Las Vegas, NV 89117
room_description: In a missing teenagers case, your detective unit stumbles upon a strange piece of evidence. It's a video of their last moments... When you start watching, you can't seem to stop, and then you are captured by the Unknown presence and taken to its lair. Will you be able to escape your fate?
